726841f-a.title: Queens: Hawtree Creek Road - 133rd Avenue
726841f-a.text:
Hawtree Creek Rd., north from One Hundred Thirty-fifth Ave. to
One Hundred Thirty-third Ave., showing in a set of three views on the
west side of the road in line of Lefferts Boulevard, the J. H. Lott
house of 1860 to 1873, subsequently acquired by William Hopkins.
Richard Wakefteld owned it in 1934.
1922
Views 1, 2, and 3.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
